725594f-a.title: Queens: 70th Road - 153rd Street
725594f-a.text:
70th Road, north side, near 153rd Street, showing the
Campbell farmhouse and barns (1891-1909). 70th Road, here,
is the former Head of the Vleigh Road. in the background
are buildings of New York City's Parental Home.
P. L. Sperr  March 23, 1927
